{
  "texts": [
    "A. Deductive Approach The data in our first demonstration includes the Twitter biographies (henceforth referred to as Twitter bios) of all politicians with a Twitter account elected to the United States Senate from 2008 to 2022.",
    "The goal of the research is to analyze the role of lifestyles in politicians' Twitter self-descriptions.",
    "As such, we need to classify the different lifestyle words present in those descriptions.",
    "After collecting the Twitter bios, the next step in the research design was to identify all the different lifestyle items present in this dataset containing 201 Twitter biographies.",
    "Annotating this many biographies manually takes time, and LLMs can save time."
  ]
}